frame Create a battle

actor Educator

activate Educator
Educator->System: 1: requestTournamentPage()
activate System
System-->Educator: 2: show(tournament-page)
deactivate System

Educator->System: 3: createNewBattle()
activate System
alt notAnEducator == true
System-->Educator: 4: show(not-educator Message)
else creatorPermission == false
System-->Educator: 5: show(no-permission Message)
else 
System-->Educator:7: returnBattleForm(form)
deactivate System

Educator->Educator:8: compileBattleForm(form)
activate System
Educator->System: 9: sendBattleForm(form)
System->System: 10 checkForm(form)
alt wrongContent == true
System-->Educator: 11: show(wrong-content Message)
else
System-->Educator: 12: ack
end
end

deactivate System
deactivate Educator
